    <item>
      <title>韩国最高政治领导人面临许多法律障碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/legal-challenges-faced-by-south-korea-s-top-political-leaders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国宪法法院将于4月4日宣布对Yoon Suk Yeol总统的弹each判决，这是他命令施加戒严的四个月后的四个月。 Yoon在数十年内释放了韩国最严重的宪法危机，他在议会推翻了韩国后的六个小时后就取消了这一举动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/legal-challenges-faced-by-south-korea-s-top-political-leaders</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 04:25:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当Lutnick推动更大的投资时，美国筹码处于困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/us-chip-grants-in-limbo-as-lutnick-pushes-for-bigger-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据八个熟悉此事的人说，商务部长霍华德·卢特尼克（Howard Lutnick）表示，他可以扣留筹码的筹款活动，因为他为联邦半导体补贴提供了一致的公司，以大大扩展其美国项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/us-chip-grants-in-limbo-as-lutnick-pushes-for-bigger-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 02:38:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国周五裁定尹恩总统的弹each</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/south-korea-to-rule-on-president-yoon-s-impeachment-on-april-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国有望就弹each总统Yoon Suk Yeol的政治命运裁决，决定是否将他永久撤离他的短暂武术法令或恢复他的命运。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/south-korea-to-rule-on-president-yoon-s-impeachment-on-april-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 01:48:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本发誓支持担心特朗普关税的企业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/trump-tariffs-may-spell-economic-crisis-for-japan-onodera-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本总理史密斯·伊斯皮邦（Shigeru Ishiba）宣布了支持措施，以帮助企业应对美国关税的影响，因为担心他们可能引发经济危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/trump-tariffs-may-spell-economic-crisis-for-japan-onodera-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 01:48:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国领导人否决法案，以扩大董事会的职责向股东</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/korea-leader-vetoes-bill-to-broaden-board-duties-to-shareholders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国代理总统否决了一项具有里程碑意义的法案，该法案将加剧公司董事会对股东的责任，并与企业集团与改革倡导者争议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/korea-leader-vetoes-bill-to-broaden-board-duties-to-shareholders</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 00:47:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，普京将“跟进”，拒绝乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-says-putin-will-follow-through-rebuffs-ukraine-on-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统撤销了他对俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京的批评，而是指责乌克兰试图重新谈判与美国进行经济协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-says-putin-will-follow-through-rebuffs-ukraine-on-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 22:34:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的中国牙套报告将为交易谈判设定阶段</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-review-of-china-trade-deal-to-add-to-xi-trump-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在习近平达平（Xi Jinping）达成了与唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）达成的第一项贸易协议后，美国官员将在可能会在高风险的一周中对北京对这种讨价还价的遵守来表达他们的看法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-review-of-china-trade-deal-to-add-to-xi-trump-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非计划以84亿美元的州财产计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/south-africa-plans-firm-to-manage-8-4-billion-of-state-property</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非公共工程部长迪恩·麦克弗森（Dean Macpherson）表示，他计划创建一家国有公司，该公司将管理政府的房地产组合，并诱使私人投资对基础设施项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/south-africa-plans-firm-to-manage-8-4-billion-of-state-property</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 14:15:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
